cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.NE 

This paper discusses reinforcement learning algorithms and their classification based on direct and indirect methods. It also compares and unifies different RL algorithms. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also touches upon control systems (cs.SY) and neural networks (cs.NE), which are also possible sub-categories.
